{"tid":127230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【影緊乜呀你？】影女模咁樣大特寫 攝影師被批：太猖狂！","createTime":"2017-02-20T03:04:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-20T03:17:55.000Z","uid":48093,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7d3b27fac22cab1e1de3c44d5c82e2b5acdc8ce7","tid":127230,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T03:04:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170220/large/1487550656_a148.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170220%2Flarge%2F1487550656_a148.jpg&h=f78b1300&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴西一個電視清談節目的攝影師涉嫌「公器私用」，拍攝一位女模特兒時，竟一味將鏡頭「聚焦」其臀部，被指猖狂。<br />\n<br />\n女模特兒步回後台時，該位攝影師有意無意間特寫她的臀部，對他個人的「喜好」毫無掩飾，但觀眾看起來頗感突兀。<br />\n<br />\n這段「明目張膽」的片段上載到互聯網後一日，已錄得逾12萬點擊，而上載者在片段說明寫道：「無恥！攝影師見心頭好即表現無遺。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FTxCFWPJ03Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFTxCFWPJ03Y&d=DRclcmm1nwuo18s%2Bf8v8PdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=f7a041ad\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FTxCFWPJ03Y</a>"},{"pid":"6981d94b369ac2d761ae523662ac0fd9e4269a3e","tid":127230,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T03:06:16.000Z","msg":"著成咁唔畀影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b7d8183d8c9ee7f854d4beb47b3675338004e9d","tid":127230,"uid":36029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T03:17:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vm86222.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVm86222.jpg&h=ba7ba127&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}